Ask HN: How long until AI shows general intelligence without failures?
text:
Large AI models sometimes exhibit extraordinary ability (e.g. see my comment history), but also obvious failures.

How long do you think it will take until very large AI models show general intelligence without any apparent failures?

A more interesting animation app, good interaction details
text:
"Dancing Particle" is an Apple Ios App that can dynamically synthesize wallpapers. It has more than 50 dynamic particle effects, each of which can generate wallpapers. You can download it in appstore.

App Name: Dancing Particle
